SYNOPSIS

Local Pairwise Alignment benchmark demo (Protein) [OPTIONS] IN OUT

DESCRIPTION

IN is a .fa / fasta input file. OUT is a txt output file.

Settings:

-tc, --threads INT

Number of threads Default: 4.
